title: Vishwanath
subTitle: Vishwanath, an honest lawyer, is framed and imprisoned due to a gangster. After his release, he sets out to seek revenge and ends up becoming a criminal.

title: Aashik Aawara
subTitle: Jai, raised by a kind thief, lives as a con artist and falls for Jyoti but his love story takes a turn when he uncovers a shocking truth about her father that changes everything.

title: Bal Ganesh 3
subTitle: Dhoti, Topi and Suit Boot are more than happy to oblige when a group of alien kids come over to listen to adventure stories about their favourite Bal Ganesh.

title: Dushmani
subTitle: Suraj and Sapna, lovers belonging to enemy families, find their relationship threatened by bullets and betrayal when their brothers collide.

title: Ek Hi Raasta
subTitle: Army officer Vikram works with terrorist Kubla and steals vital army information for him. In the process, he ends up killing a colleague and pins the blame on a fellow soldier.

title: Garv: Pride and Honour
subTitle: An honest officer falls prey to a corrupt system where he is dismissed from the police force for getting involved in a murder case while trying to arrest a few corrupt politicians.

title: Sholay
subTitle: Jai and Veeru, two ex-convicts, are hired by Thakur Baldev Singh, a retired policeman, to help him nab Gabbar Singh, a notorious dacoit, who has spread havoc in the village of Ramgarh.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Tejaa
subTitle: Tejaa's family gets murdered when he is a child. Later, in an attempt to seek revenge, he traces down the three goons who were responsible.

title: Naina
subTitle: After years of blindness caused by an accident, Naina gets a successful cornea transplant. However, she soon begins to see terrifying visions that prompt her to investigate the source of her sight.

title: Fun2ssh
subTitle: Three men accidentally end up in the 10th century while being on the run. As they navigate the new world, they attempt to go back home and prove their innocence.

title: Dulhan Hum Le Jayenge
subTitle: Sapna is raised by her three uncles, each one of them with a contrasting pursuit in life. She falls in love with Raja, who tries to impress each of her uncles in a different manner.

title: Darr
subTitle: Swept up in a whirlwind of fear and romance, Kiran teeters on the edge of a mental and emotional precipice. While Sunil keeps holding on to her, Rahul spares no effort to drag her down with himself.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Stree 2
subTitle: When Sarkata, a headless spirit, starts snatching the women of Chanderi away into a petrifying parallel realm, Vicky and his friends must save the day.

title: Zulmi
subTitle: Raj is hired as a bodyguard for Komal, and the two grow closer to each other over time. However, things get complicated when he comes across Nihal, the man who molested his sister.

title: Zulmi
subTitle: Raj is hired as a bodyguard for Komal, and the two grow closer to each other over time. However, things get complicated when he comes across Nihal, the man who molested his sister.

title: Yugpurush
subTitle: Anirudh is discharged from an asylum after 20 years of treatment. Although he still struggles to adjust to the normal world, he finds comfort with Sunita.

title: Lamhaa
subTitle: Vikram, an Indian intelligence agent, is sent to Kashmir to investigate the people responsible for a host of extremist attacks. In his mission, he receives help from a young woman named Aziza.

title: Hanuman Da' Damdaar
subTitle: A young boy, sets out to make his father proud by embarking on a series of jungle adventure which leads him to metamorphose in to Hanuman.

title: Vidhaata
subTitle: After the death of his parent, Kunal lives with his grandfather Shamsher. However, when he falls in love with Durga, Shamsher plans to separate them.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: Thakur marries his mistress when his first wife, Pooja, is unable to bear children. His brother-in-law opposes this marriage to save the dignity of his sister and fights to reunite them.

title: Haqeeqat
subTitle: Shiva changes his name to Ajay as he leaves his criminal life after saving a police officer and his family. He falls in love with a widow and marries her, but his past comes back to haunt him.

title: Aunty No. 1
subTitle: To help his friends, Gopi dresses up as their aunt to solve their problems. However, he gets into a hilarious situation where he must avoid two suitors trying to woo him.

title: Vardi
subTitle: Constable Bhagwan is killed by Lalchand, a gangster. Years later, Bhagwan's son Ajay, along with his father's close associate Inspector Verma, tries to capture Lalchand and bring him to justice.

title: Apmaan Ki Aag
subTitle: While celebrating his girlfriend Mona's birthday, Vikrant gets humiliated by two goons. He vows to exact revenge but it takes him down a difficult and thorny path.
